title: Brahms - Symphony No. 4 - Abbado, BPO
description:
Brahms: Variations on a Theme of Haydn, Nanie (for chorus and orchestra), Symphony No. 4.

Johannes Brahms' Fourth Symphony, Variations on a Theme of Haydn, and Nanie, performed by the Berlin Philharmonic Orchestra under Claudio Abbado, and released by DG in 1992. This version of Brahms' final symphonic utterance may well become your favourite.

Please enjoy.
